### Get all users (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get users with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get users with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users?search=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get users with active filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users?is_active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get users with sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users?sort_by=created_at&sort_dir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get users with all filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users?page=1&limit=10&search=user&is_active=true&sort_by=email&sort_dir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get users without authentication (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users
